<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٣٩٩ - أَبُو حريش.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> زيد بن مُحَمَّد الْعمريّ ,<span class="c5"> اسْمه:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>مُعَاوِيَة.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> مُحَمَّد بن الْحسن الْأَسدي ,<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَعبيد الله بن مُوسَى.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>٢٤٠٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حجر:</span> عداده فِي أهل مصر.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> اللَّيْث بن سعد.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>قَالَه لي أَبُو سعيد بن يُونُس بن عبد الْأَعْلَى.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>٢٤٠١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حجر:</span> حبيب بن حجر الْقَيْسِي<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> ثَابت الْبنانِيّ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>كناه روح بن عبَادَة.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>٢٤٠٢ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حجر:</span> الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">عَن:</span> عَمْرو بن قيس الْملَائي.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c5">روى حَدِيثه:</span> الْحسن بن عَرَفَة , عَن عمَارَة بن<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>مُحَمَّد عَنهُ.<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>٢٤٠٣ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حجر:</span> عَمْرو بن رَافع<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>الْقزْوِينِي.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> جرير بن عبد الحميد.<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> أَبُو حَاتِم , وَأَبُو زرْعَة.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>حَدثنَا أَحْمد بن مُحَمَّد بن إِبْرَاهِيم مولى بني<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p22"></span>هَاشم , ثَنَا أَبُو حَاتِم مُحَمَّد بن إِدْرِيس , ثَنَا<a href="#p22" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p23"></span>أَبُو حجر عَمْرو بن رَافع الْقزْوِينِي.<a href="#p23" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p24"></span>٢٤٠٤ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حرمل:</span> الْكُوفِي.<a href="#p24" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p25"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> عبَادَة بن الْوَلِيد.<a href="#p25" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p26"></span>روى <span class="c4">[عَنهُ]</span> : إِسْرَائِيل بن يُونُس.<a href="#p26" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p27"></span>٢٤٠٥ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حكيمة:</span> الغزال , بَصرِي.<a href="#p27" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p28"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> أبي عُثْمَان النَّهْدِيّ.<a href="#p28" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p29"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> حَمَّاد بن سَلمَة , وَهِشَام<a href="#p29" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p30"></span>الدستوَائي.<a href="#p30" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p31"></span>٢٤٠٦ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حكيمة:</span> الْبَصْرِيّ.<a href="#p31" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p32"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> سَلام بن مِسْكين.<a href="#p32" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p33"></span>هُوَ الأول.<a href="#p33" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p34"></span>٢٤٠٧ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حذافة:</span> ابْن قيس.<a href="#p34" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p35"></span>لَهُ صُحْبَة.<a href="#p35" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p36"></span>٢٤٠٨ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حذافة:</span> أَحْمد بن إِسْمَاعِيل<a href="#p36" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p37"></span>السَّهْمِي.<a href="#p37" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p38"></span><span class="c5">حدث عَن:</span> مَالك بن أنس , وَابْن أبي الزِّنَاد.<a href="#p38" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p39"></span>٢٤٠٩ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حِوَالَة:</span> عبد الله بن حِوَالَة.<a href="#p39" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p40"></span>لَهُ صُحْبَة , نزل الْأُرْدُن.<a href="#p40" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p41"></span>كناه القباني , عَن أَحْمد بن سعيد الدَّارمِيّ.<a href="#p41" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p42"></span>٢٤١٠ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو الْحَمْرَاء:</span> هِلَال بن الْحَارِث.<a href="#p42" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p43"></span>لَهُ صُحْبَة.<a href="#p43" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p44"></span><span class="c5">روى عَنهُ:</span> أَبُو دَاوُد النَّخعِيّ.<a href="#p44" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p45"></span>وَسمعت مُحَمَّد بن يَعْقُوب ,<span class="c5"> يَقُول:</span> سَمِعت<a href="#p45" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p46"></span>عباسا , سَمِعت <span class="c2">(ق ١٠٢ / أ)</span> يحيى بن معِين<a href="#p46" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p47"></span><span class="c5">يَقُول:</span> أَبُو الْحَمْرَاء اسْمه: هِلَال بن الْحَارِث.<a href="#p47" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p48"></span>٢٤١١ -<span class="c5"> أَبُو حَدْرَد:</span> سَلامَة بن عُمَيْر بن أبي<a href="#p48" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p49"></span>سَلامَة الْأَسْلَمِيّ.<a href="#p49" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p50"></span>لَهُ صُحْبَة.<a href="#p50" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p51"></span>أخبرنَا أَحْمد بن مهْرَان , وَأحمد بن<a href="#p51" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p52"></span>عُثْمَان الْأَبْهَرِيّ ,<span class="c5"> قَالَا:</span> ثَنَا مُوسَى , ثَنَا<a href="#p52" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>